---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/WideBase.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "Welcome to Cumberland University's student-run newspaper, Helios!",
	title: "Helios - Cumberland University",
};

// Import images from the assets directory
import image1 from "../assets/firepit.png";
import image2 from "../assets/firepit.png";
import image3 from "../assets/tower.png";
import image4 from "../assets/logo.png";
---
<BaseLayout meta={meta}>
	<section style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem; background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0); color: white; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);">
		<h1 style="font-weight: bold;">Welcome to Cumberland University's very own student-run magazine, Helios!</h1>
		<p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 1rem; font-weight: bold;">
			Stay informed with the latest news, stories, and updates from our talented student journalists.
		</p>
	</section>
	<section style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; padding: 2rem; align-items: center;">
		<img 
			src={image1.src} 
			alt="Image 1" 
			style="width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);" 
		/>
		<div style="padding: 1rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); align-self: start;">
			<h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Who Are We?</h2>
			<p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
				Hello! We are Helios, a student-run magazine from Cumberland University in Lebanon, Tennessee. Our mission is to serve as the voice of the student body, providing a platform for creative expression, insightful journalism, and meaningful storytelling. We are passionate about keeping our campus community informed and engaged with the latest news, stories, and updates that matter most to students, faculty, and staff alike.
			</p>
			<p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 1rem;">
				At Helios, we believe in the power of words to inspire, educate, and connect. Our dedicated team of student journalists works tirelessly to bring you a diverse range of content, from in-depth investigative pieces and opinion articles to lighthearted features and event coverage. Whether it's breaking news, campus developments, or stories that celebrate the achievements of our peers, we strive to deliver content that resonates with our readers.
			</p>
			<p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 1rem;">
				We take pride in being a publication that reflects the vibrant and dynamic spirit of Cumberland University. Our magazine is not just about reporting facts; it's about telling stories that capture the essence of our community. Through our work, we aim to foster a sense of belonging and unity among students while also encouraging critical thinking and open dialogue on important issues.
			</p>
			<p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 1rem;">
				Thank you for supporting Helios. We are excited to continue growing and evolving as a publication, and we invite you to join us on this journey. Whether you're a reader, a contributor, or simply someone curious about what we do, we welcome you to be a part of our story. Together, let's shine a light on the stories that make Cumberland University truly special.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section style="padding: 2rem;">
		<h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: center;">Meet Our Team</h2>
		<ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
			<li style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid white; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
				<div style="width: 2px; height: 50px; background-color: white; margin-right: 1rem; border: 1px solid white; border-radius: 4px;"></div>
				<div>
					<strong style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Isaiah Crace</strong>
					<p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">The developer of the site, enthusiastic about programming and technology.</p>
				</div>
			</li>
			<li style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid white; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
				<div style="width: 2px; height: 50px; background-color: white; margin-right: 1rem; border: 1px solid white; border-radius: 4px;"></div>
				<div>
					<strong style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Thomas Jefferson</strong>
					<p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">Passionate about education and innovation, sharing insights on campus developments.</p>
				</div>
			</li>
			<li style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid white; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
				<div style="width: 2px; height: 50px; background-color: white; margin-right: 1rem; border: 1px solid white; border-radius: 4px;"></div>
				<div>
					<strong style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Abraham Lincoln</strong>
					<p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">Focused on equality and justice, covering stories that inspire change.</p>
				</div>
			</li>
			<li style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid white; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
				<div style="width: 2px; height: 50px; background-color: white; margin-right: 1rem; border: 1px solid white; border-radius: 4px;"></div>
				<div>
					<strong style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Theodore Roosevelt</strong>
					<p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">An adventurer at heart, writing about outdoor activities and campus events.</p>
				</div>
			</li>
			<li style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid white; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
				<div style="width: 2px; height: 50px; background-color: white; margin-right: 1rem; border: 1px solid white; border-radius: 4px;"></div>
				<div>
					<strong style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Franklin D. Roosevelt</strong>
					<p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">Dedicated to community welfare, highlighting student achievements and initiatives.</p>
				</div>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
